# Claude Zombies - multi-floor demo map
#
# Demonstrates vertical / overlapping floors (docs/multi-floor-maps.md).
# New map entry:
#   FLOOR x z sx sz y               flat walkable surface at height y
#   FLOOR x z sx sz yLow yHigh X|Z  ramp sloping yLow->yHigh along X or Z
# An implicit ground plane at Y=0 always exists, so the arena floor is the
# downstairs; FLOOR lines add decks/ramps above it. Standing on the ground
# under the deck keeps you at Y=0; walking up the ramp puts you on the deck
# at Y=4 — a true overlapping upstairs/downstairs.

NAME Multi-Floor Demo

ATMOSPHERE
    fog       18 22 35  14 70
    sky_tint  255 255 255
END

# --- Spawns (ground level) --------------------------------------------
SPAWN  0 0
SPAWN  2 0
SPAWN -2 0
SPAWN  0 2

# --- Elevated deck over the eastern half (Y = 4) ----------------------
FLOOR  15 -10   18 18   4

# --- Ramp from the ground (Y0) up to the deck (Y4), sloping along +X ---
# spans x[-2..6] at z=-10; low edge meets the ground, high edge meets deck.
FLOOR   2 -10    8 6    0 4 X

# --- A smaller catwalk higher still, reached from the deck ------------
FLOOR  15  12   12 8    4
FLOOR  15   2    8 4    4 8 Z      # ramp from deck (Y4) up to catwalk (Y8)
FLOOR  15  20   12 6    8          # top catwalk at Y8

# --- A few ground obstacles for cover ---------------------------------
OBSTACLE -12 -8    6 3
OBSTACLE -20  12   5 5 3
OBSTACLE -10  20   4 4 3

# --- Wall buys --------------------------------------------------------
WALLBUY -39.45 18     +x  SMG
WALLBUY -15   -39.45  +z  RIFLE

# --- Windows (zombie entries) -----------------------------------------
WINDOW -40   -8   +x
WINDOW -18   40   -z

# --- Perks ------------------------------------------------------------
PERK  -8  12 JUG
PERK   4  -8 SPEED

# --- Mystery box + Pack-a-Punch ---------------------------------------
MBOX -22 15
PAP  -25 -20
